    {
      "type": "action",
      "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/ThreeActions.webp",
      "name": "Flickering Form",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Asyra can switch from her normal form to a less substantial flickering form. While in her flickering form, she gains resistance 5 to all damage (except force and negative). However, Asyra can't use any of her Strikes or actions requiring a fully physical form like @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Grapple]{Grapple}, @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Shove]{Shove}, or @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Trip]{Trip}. Asyra can switch back to her normal form as a single action, which also has the concentrate trait.</p>"
        },
